  <brief_title>Randomized Trial to Evaluate the Effectiveness of Nurse Case Management</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Trial to Evaluate the Effectiveness of Nurse Case Management on High-Risk Pregnancy Outcomes</official_title>
